@page
@model AnotherNightmare.Pages.ThirdSceneModel

<div class="third-scene-background">
    <h1 class="scene-title">Meeting at the Haarp Facility</h1>
    <p class="scene-text">
        As you step inside, the door shuts ominously behind you. Matthews begins to explain the facility's capabilities, hinting at experiments that push the boundaries of science and ethics. The conversation takes a sudden turn when she reveals a controversial experiment scheduled for today, one that could have unforeseen consequences. The decision on whether to proceed rests with you, and time is running out
    </p>

    <!-- Choices -->
    <div class="choices">
        <form method="post">
            <button type="submit" name="choice" value="1" class="choice-button">Authorize the Experiment </button>
            <button type="submit" name="choice" value="2" class="choice-button">Consult with Dr. Zhao </button>
            <button type="submit" name="choice" value="3" class="choice-button">Discuss with Jake Sullivan</button>
            <button type="submit" name="choice" value="4" class="choice-button">Demand Immediate Shutdown</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>